title: Valar Rereadis: The Winds of Winter Review (w/Nina Friel)
description:
Nina Friel (goodqueenaly.tumblr.com) joins us to discuss what we've seen as a whole in TWOW so far, the Riverlands/Westerlands Prologue, the Asha Fragment, the Stark Succession and a variety of other questions!
